Day 3
Conditional Statments, Logical operators, code blocks and Scope

Conditional statements (Do check the indentation for the statements)
if Condition:
	do this
else:
	do this
	
Comparision operators
> greater than
< lesser than
>= greater than or equal to 
<= less than or equal to 
== equal to 
!= not equal to 
---

Nested if/else
if condition:
	do this
	if condition:
		do this
	else:
		do this
else: 
	do this
---
	
If/elif/else

if condition:
	do this
elif condition:
	do this
else
	do this
---

Logical Operators:

and -> if a and b -> true/false 
or  -> if a or b -> true/false
not -> if not a -> true/false

Third program (Treasure Hunt)

